  slug: "hospitalization",
  title: "Mental Health Hospitalization: When It Is Necessary and What to Expect",
  category: "Mental Health",
  categorySlug: "mental-health",
  aliases: ["psychiatric-hospital-care"],
  description: "A detailed guide to understanding psychiatric hospitalization, including voluntary and involuntary admission processes.",
